(index.html) using ONLY plain HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

This page is a CPA marketing landing page designed to unlock a reward
by redirecting users to a content locker.

STRICT REQUIREMENTS:
- Output ONLY code
- No explanations
- No markdown
- No comments outside the code
- Code must be ready to upload to GitHub Pages

PAGE STRUCTURE:
- Modern, clean, mobile-first design
- Centered layout
- Inspired by simple “claim reward” landing pages
- Fast loading and responsive

CONTENT:
- Headline: “Unlock Your Reward”
